data.description: ABSULUTELY STUNNING & READY TO MOVE IN!! sitting on almost a 1/2 acre!! This is NOT your typical bi-level. As you enter you will be welcomed by the amazingly large foyer, with your choice of entering the beautiful upper level that is graced with a large living room and kitchen that screams let's entertain, especially when you see the glass doors leading to your ample size wood deck. Vaulted ceilings are an added amenity. The lower level offers a very generous sized rec room, 2 bedrooms and a walk-out patio. Finished laundry, and Lots of storage are a plus. Storage shed, 2 1/2 car attached garage, AND Rolling Prairie Schools. What more could you ask for at this price. This charming home will not disappoint!! You will feel the love when you enter this beautiful home. Make you appt to see this beauty!!!
